name: AIRSMIX
description:
AnythingV3 In Realistic Style Mix

Two merged model base on AnythingV3

AIRSMIX_A: Anime Style, similar as AnythingV3 with more depth, less flat.

AIRSMIX_R: Realistic style, similar as AIRSMIX_A, still have some animeish.

Models have embedded VAE

WD1.4 VAE for AIRSMIX_A and SD1.5 VAE for AIRSMIX_R.

all previews images have same prompt and seed for each model, use no hires fix or inpainting.
